\taxon{Definition}
\title{Local satisfaction relation}
\import{macro}

\p{
  For a distributive lattice #{D}, we define the \em{satisfaction relation} as follows: For #{x\in\spec D} and #{a\in D}, we define
  ##{ x \models a \eff a \in x. }
  In other words, #{x \models a} iff #{a = 1} in the [local algebra](idem-comm-IHKN) #{D/x}.
}